    <item>
      <title>Docs: Twitter</title>
      <link>https://hugo-for-newbie.kejyun.com/docs/content/short-code/twitter/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Apr 2021 08:50:29 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://hugo-for-newbie.kejyun.com/docs/content/short-code/twitter/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h2 id=&#34;用法&#34;&gt;用法&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;{{ &amp;lt; tweet (編號) &amp;gt; }}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;{{ &amp;lt; tweet 1181536841666682880 &amp;gt; }}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;範例&#34;&gt;範例&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;找一個你想要內嵌的 Twitter 文章，然後複製網址後方的文章代碼，像是下方的 &lt;code&gt;1181536841666682880&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;https://twitter.com/marie_kitsunebi/status/1181536841666682880
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;然後使用 Twitter Shortcodes 就可以在內文中內嵌 Twitter 文章&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;en&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;The lanterns of Jiufen at sunset... They weren’t lit yet when I took this photo, but the sun lit them for me&lt;br&gt;🏮🏮🏮&lt;br&gt;It really looked just like the scene in Spirited Away!&lt;br&gt;What’s your favorite Ghibli movie?&lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/Taiwan?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#Taiwan&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/SpiritedAway?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#SpiritedAway&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/Ghibli?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#Ghibli&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/jWQGB7ZcMA&#34;&gt;pic.twitter.com/jWQGB7ZcMA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Marie🦊 (@marie_kitsunebi) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/marie_kitsunebi/status/1181536841666682880?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;October 8, 2019&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;script async src=&#34;https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;

